Subject: [MediaTek] NEA Web Console Reports Data - Limited to 1000
Description:
Hi Saqib,

After rebuilding the folder of Report,it worked out to generate report,but unfortunately,it looks like the output of report like CSV file has a limitation for exporting all records.

As for this,please assist in checking it out and make it clear.

Thank you for your cooperation.

Jimmy
Solution_Comment__c: Reports -> Configure -> Widgets. Select Grid Type and hit Configure. Select All Rows and All Columns under Export CSV Options Head.
